        "text": "2 Chronicles 1:12",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ", and signifies that Jehoshaphat, like his ancestors David and Solomon, was blessed for walking in the pious ways of these his forefathers. ",
        "children": []
      }
    ]
  }
